{"tid":1708534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"前大學教授：因為手無寸鐵，所以開槍囉。","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:23:57.000Z","uid":69753,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87886cc9f6ac6dc835f87d5b027187a7ffc8fae7","tid":1708534,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpNTOe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpNTOe8.jpg&h=a3f23bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友：差人向手無寸鐵的示威者開槍啊！<br />\n前大學教授：因為手無寸鐵，所以開槍囉。你幾時見差人向持有竹竿及大棍的示威者開槍？<br />\n大家記得之前在元朗及天水圍的械鬥嗎？差人無開槍喔，反而且戰且走。<br />\n止戈為武的意思，就是說，如果你擁有制衡對方的武力，你可以停止武力，達致和平。如果你沒有這種武力而去挑釁軍隊，你得到的，是射殺或俘虜。如果運氣好，是俘虜之後輪姦虐待，之後射殺。<br />\n沒有這種制衡能力之前，返屋企休息睡覺啦。"},{"pid":"f11fceec3a3bd4db2793374d2cbf2827f9bfa918","tid":1708534,"uid":88937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"因為欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"0aa82855131d219a75a04d8280c0d6c04169f62e","tid":1708534,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11fceec3a3bd4db2793374d2cbf2827f9bfa918","tid":1708534,"uid":88937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"因為欺善怕惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡。四字成語可以解釋好多現象。"},{"pid":"e298f760f301830e126c6ea8e4a231bc718ee9ad","tid":1708534,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"將吃眼前虧，視為撚狗，不是勇敢，不是報仇，不是反抗，是無知，是找死。"},{"pid":"29cfc4e471472f7b57e13846afed80431396c4d5","tid":1708534,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"魔差知道行暴無後果，就更加大膽行暴。當知道殺敵一百、會招致自損八十，就會有所顧忌。"},{"pid":"39b8e30363211e3f70e9f1a96c8cff0ae0beaac6","tid":1708534,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQBmcKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F